{"tid":1733654,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［重開］我想救Poly手足同埋佢屋企人","createTime":"2019-11-18T07:01:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-18T09:26:42.000Z","uid":35065,"like":127,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":63,"replies":[{"pid":"e4e9974ee6abbbe89cd09f2e2c3218846f8392b6","tid":1733654,"uid":35065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T07:01:03.000Z","msg":"所有Polyu 手足嘅朋友 即刻聯絡手足家人<br />\n立即向傳媒(蘋果)備案<br />\n表達自己仔女失左蹤 （唔好講話身處Polyu)<br />\n同時為 佢自己 同埋 手足 立不自殺聲明<br />\n<br />\n成個活動以來半個家長都無出過聲<br />\n因為啲狗嘅滅聲工作一早就好完善<br />\n所以要早啲狗一步 搵傳媒備案<br />\n萬一出左事走唔甩 手足都唔可以白白被虐死/變浮屍<br />\n同時保障家人唔會被滅聲<br />\n<br />\n事到如今Poly手足根本唔怕被知身份<br />\n乜撚野怕自爆嘅唔該收皮 <br />\n傳媒（蘋果）根本無理由（無犯法）亦無能力去拉家長<br />\n<br />\n唔該幫手推 <br />\n要保住手足 亦要保住佢家人<br />\n任何前線手足都可以用呢個方法搵朋友留個底 <br />\n以防日後被捕"},{"pid":"68d6c4429b9fe45f0b8a0329df454ba6c1a2bd63","tid":1733654,"uid":35065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T07:01:13.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e7a08426ab524569542541f19a6f6e493474a390","tid":1733654,"uid":35065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T07:01:26.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"dd13428f7122f98ce99d78bd6b79abe52a2da3b7","tid":1733654,"uid":35065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T07:01:58.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"3601b75f337f15969f46e992fadcf4a6c4a641f7","tid":1733654,"uid":35065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T07:02:31.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0e61b263b28f58fe5fab77156bcb5d2e0883c138","tid":1733654,"uid":35065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T07:02:47.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">唔該，幫手推</span>"},{"pid":"29de03ba495ca95930b1f1d59991d04748658996","tid":1733654,"uid":35065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T07:03:06.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6ae54bcf70fba8b8235cad1fbdd66f2453d63b2d","tid":1733654,"uid":35065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T07:03:16.000Z","msg